      "text": "NON-FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS: 4Min\n\n1} LATENCY: \n100-200ms\n\n2} SCALABILITY:\n10M customers per day\nmaking payment -> 115 request/sec\nsaving_card -> 115 request/sec\n230 request/sec\n\n3} Highly available\n\n4} Failure Tolerant\n\n\n",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "lHeLS_0Z5wIRvcGIWWaQA",
      "originalText": "NON-FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS: 4Min\n\n1} LATENCY: \n100-200ms\n\n2} SCALABILITY:\n10M customers per day\nmaking payment -> 115 request/sec\nsaving_card -> 115 request/sec\n230 request/sec\n\n3} Highly available\n\n4} Failure Tolerant\n\n\n",
