      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "text": "API-Endpoints: 5Min\n\n1] API_NAME:  POST - save_payment_details \n\nA} Input: user_id, user_name, user_address, credit\ncard/debit card/UPI\n\nB} Output:- COMPLETED, FAILED\n2] API_NAME:  POST - make_payment \n\nA} Input: payment_details\n\nB} Output:- COMPLETED, IN-Review, FAILED\n\n2] API_NAME:  POST - payment_outflow \n\nA} Input: payment_details\n\nB} Output:- COMPLETED, IN-Review, FAILED\n\n\n\n",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "MRIPLh6vB6a5v5dU-hedj",
      "originalText": "API-Endpoints: 5Min\n\n1] API_NAME:  POST - save_payment_details \n\nA} Input: user_id, user_name, user_address, credit card/debit card/UPI\n\nB} Output:- COMPLETED, FAILED\n2] API_NAME:  POST - make_payment \n\nA} Input: payment_details\n\nB} Output:- COMPLETED, IN-Review, FAILED\n\n2] API_NAME:  POST - payment_outflow \n\nA} Input: payment_details\n\nB} Output:- COMPLETED, IN-Review, FAILED\n\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
